<p>The NSW Design System Community forum will close on 29 July 2026. The forum will remain available until then.</p>

<p>After this date, the forum will no longer be accessible. If you need information from an existing discussion, save a copy before 29 July 2026.</p>

<p>For questions about using the NSW Design System, contact <a href="mailto:designsystem@customerservice.nsw.gov.au">designsystem@customerservice.nsw.gov.au</a>.</p>

<p>To report a bug or technical issue, <a href="https://github.com/digitalnsw/nsw-design-system/issues/new" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">raise a GitHub issue</a>.</p>
